{"tid":1223541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"撐修例運動呢？","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T17:56:06.000Z","uid":133435,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"415818e4603196d977a35dc767f1295cf0115865","tid":1223541,"uid":133435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"連二連三有大型既反修例遊行同示威，但事實仲有唔少人其實係撐修例既<br />\n<br />\n咁耐以黎除左聯署，撐修例既群眾究竟有咩方式去表達意見？<br />\n<br />\n撐修例既人，好似從來冇確確實實，走出黎，透過行動，傳遞畀大家知佢地既立場，佢地既見解，佢地要立例既決心<br />\n<br />\n如果哩度有撐修例既人，我尊重你地既立場，你地有你地既立場，原因去支持，但同時請你地用行動去說服香港人，要令到反修例既人心悅誠服，就請你拎出比反修例人士更多既汗水同行動。<br />\n<br />\n如果你到哩一刻都係支持修例既，請上街話畀香港人知！"},{"pid":"3bbb2a55e8ab9076ceee3ca691f4781250e083b7","tid":1223541,"uid":63240,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cauxj6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCauxj6F.png&h=4a8aceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢九十幾萬人裡面 有兩萬個真係會走出黎已經偷笑啦"},{"pid":"f1a2e92855d3e5f3ed2db037e76631c838f5a9d4","tid":1223541,"uid":133435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3bbb2a55e8ab9076ceee3ca691f4781250e083b7","tid":1223541,"uid":63240,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cauxj6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCauxj6F.png&h=4a8aceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢九十幾萬人裡面 有兩萬個真係會走出黎已經偷笑啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"老老實實，如果個兩萬人肯出黎既，佢地絕對比其餘91萬值得尊重"},{"pid":"72b90bf2447ae5d33e4da87708c033bfabb58a3d","tid":1223541,"uid":212336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:42:21.000Z","msg":"無錢收就緊係縮返入佢老母個閪到啦"},{"pid":"4426339c4e85c7e66d826a2db77514a86b3db5a8","tid":1223541,"uid":50483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1a2e92855d3e5f3ed2db037e76631c838f5a9d4","tid":1223541,"uid":133435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3bbb2a55e8ab9076